---
subtitle: What are you doing now?
description: What am I up to? It's not too personal, but if you want to nerd out, let's nerd out!
layout: layouts/base.njk
stylesheets: /css/now-styles.css
scripts: /js/now-scripts.js
---

{# page scripts #}

<section id="now-section" data-au="flex-container">
  <div id="now-info-container" data-au="set-width">
    <div class="page-nav">
      <p>&lt;&nbsp; <a class="text-link" href="/index.html">Return to Portfolio</a></p>
    </div>
      
    <h2>Sammy, what are you up to?</h2>
    <p>It's not that "I have a lot going on" &mdash; it's that "there's a lot I'm trying to do." My hands may be pretty full, but as long as it doesn't cross into the dreaded 'overwhelming' territory, we'll be just fine.</p>
    <p><a class="text-link" href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank">Learn more</a> about the <a href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank"><code>/now</code></a> webpage movement.</p>
  </div>

  <div data-items-container class="flex-width now-items-container">

    {# populate with non-expired #}
    {% for item in now.nowItems | notExpired %}
      <div class="item-row now-row">
        <div class="item-header" data-au="flex-container align-center">
          <div class="item-category-container" data-au="flex-container">
            {% if item.itemCategory == "tb" %}
              <a class="item-category-badge terrabyte-badge" href="https://www.terrabyte.eco" target="_blank">
                <span>Terrabyte</span>
              </a>
            {% elif item.itemCategory == "ghm" %}
              <a class="item-category-badge goldenharpmedia-badge" href="https://www.goldenharpmedia.com" target="_blank">
                <span>Golden Harp Media</span>
              </a>
            {% else %}
              <a class="item-category-badge personal-badge" href="https://www.sammyharper.com">
                <span>Personal</span>
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <h3 class="" data-item-title>{{ item.itemTitle }}</h3>
        </div>

        <p>{{ item.itemCaption }}</p>

        {% if item.linkHref %}
          <a class="text-link" href="{{ item.linkHref }}" target="_blank">{{ item.linkTitle }}</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>